"None"	"None"	"MRI"	"pCASL: ASL"	"HCA8271980_V1_MR_UnprocPcasl_manifest.json"	""	"mbPCASLhr Unprocessed"	"HCP-A Mapping the Human Connectome During Typical Aging "
"2847"	"300019"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVHU365WWJ"	"HCA8267383"	"04/01/2018"	"952"	"M"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." "2847"	"300926"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVCG013TG3"	"HCA9551991"	"10/01/2017"	"770"	"M"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. "2847"	"300813"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVZA681FUH"	"HCA9435080"	"04/01/2018"	"496"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. "2847"	"299919"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVLX244NJX"	"HCA8127165"	"04/01/2017"	"688"	"M"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." "2847"	"301066"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVVR659NMT"	"HCA9735294"	"04/01/2018"	"870"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. "2847"	"300358"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVNV982YP2"	"HCA8720983"	"10/01/2017"	"945"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). "2847"	"301083"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVHE221BTD"	"HCA9750290"	"10/01/2017"	"438"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). "2847"	"300071"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVCY934KKX"	"HCA8335778"	"07/01/2018"	"462"	"M"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." "2847"	"300622"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVHN378UZE"	"HCA9157179"	"07/01/2018"	"480"	"M"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. "2847"	"300749"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVER501CRF"	"HCA9342578"	"10/01/2017"	"858"	"M"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). "2847"	"301003"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVBK696XTD"	"HCA9641386"	"04/01/2019"	"880"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." "2847"	"300110"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVMD441YEF"	"HCA8369896"	"01/01/2019"	"542"	"M"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." "2847"	"300772"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVHZ224HLY"	"HCA9373589"	"01/01/2019"	"1200"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. "2847"	"301021"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVFP567XT8"	"HCA9677509"	"01/01/2018"	"589"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. "2847"	"299670"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVKZ865HK8"	"HCA7705275"	"07/01/2018"	"483"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." "2847"	"298699"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVPD999MA1"	"HCA6465175"	"04/01/2017"	"489"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." "2847"	"298956"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVKX343XHB"	"HCA6746284"	"07/01/2017"	"728"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). "2847"	"298723"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVCM290JK2"	"HCA6498190"	"07/01/2018"	"677"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." "2847"	"298619"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVLF064CXV"	"HCA6320048"	"10/01/2017"	"592"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. "2847"	"299112"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVTR398KRC"	"HCA6963696"	"07/01/2019"	"869"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." "2847"	"299494"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVPB704AZ4"	"HCA7492486"	"04/01/2018"	"531"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. "2847"	"298641"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVCK171TEL"	"HCA6374576"	"01/01/2017"	"665"	"M"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." "2847"	"299252"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVMZ809NHR"	"HCA7155973"	"10/01/2017"	"869"	"F"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." "2847"	"299401"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVPW375KC9"	"HCA7348277"	"10/01/2017"	"700"	"M"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). "2847"	"298668"	"35476"	"NDAR_INVFH192BPE"	"HCA6429272"	"04/01/2017"	"716"	"M"	"This package contains multi-echo MPRAGE (T1 weighted) and T2-SPACE (T2 weighted) scans (in NIFTI format). The T1w image reconstruction of the mean of the first two echoes of the multi-echo T1w scan and the T2w image, both acquired with volumetric navigators (vNav) for real-time motion correction, but collected without Siemen's 'Prescan Normalize' feature, are recommended and were used as the starting point for Structural preprocessing. It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit." It also includes the associated navigators for each scan, reconstructions of each of the four separate echoes from the multi-echo T1w scan, reconstructions of the RMS of the four T1w echoes, and a session report file that provides an overview of the usable imaging data collected during the participant's visit."
